ckmelon may use personal information/details/data for new and unanticipated uses not previously disclosed in Blackmelon’s Privacy Policy. If our information/details/data practices change regarding information/details/data previously collected, Blackmelon shall make reasonable efforts to provide notice and obtain consent of any such uses as may be required by law.
